text: 1st Class 2nd Class The Order of Saint Nicholas Thaumaturgus () is a Ukrainian order awarded, as the inscription says (in Ukrainian): "For the Multiplying of the Good on the Earth", issued by the Foundation of International Awards ("Фонд міжнародних премій"), Ukraine."Фонд міжнародних премій" (retrieved May 9 2016) ==Recipients== *Taisia Povaliy, Ukrainian singer, 1998 ==References== Category:Orders, decorations, and medals of Ukraine
title: Order of Saint Nicholas Thaumaturgus (International)
